            , was indicted for <rs id="t17831210-23-off137" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17831210-23-off137" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17831210-23-off137" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t17831210-23-cd138" type="crimeDate">2d of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17831210-23-off137 t17831210-23-cd138"></join> last, one pair of linen sheets, value 8 s. two pillow-cases, value 2 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17831210-23-victim342" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Hibbett
                        <interp inst="t17831210-23-victim342" type="surname" value="Hibbett"></interp>
